  • Classes in models used by factories 
    Class and Description
    WorkSpaceGraphElement
    A class which represents the data relating to a single element in a WorkSpace All elements which contain the data modeling a data structure element in a work space (LinkedList Heads, Arrays, Nodes etc) will all extend this class.
